##############################################################################################
PIC (Pausing Index Calculator): quick calculation of pausing index of genes of next-generation sequencing data.

Package: PIC
Type: Package
Version: 1.0
Date: 2017-06-06
Author: Jiahuan Chen
Depends: samtools, bedtools
Maintainer: Jiahuan Chen <chenjiahuan@sjtu.edu.cn or yydq2686@126.com>

Shanghai Center for Systems Biomedicine, Shanghai Jiao Tong University
##############################################################################################


Brief:
Pausing is an essential process in gene transcription, particularly in signal-responsive pathways.
We thus developed this program to help you calculate Pausing Index of genes. For detailed 
manipulation, please refers to "README.md‚Äù.


Enjoy and thanks for your precious feedback!   